<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Schedule Conflict</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5; /* Neutral background color */
            color: #333; /* Dark text for readability */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #d9534f; /* Red for error or conflict */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #6a0dad; /* Lavender button */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #8a4eaf; /* Darker lavender for hover effect */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(138, 78, 175, 0.3);
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            a {
                font-size: 14px;
                padding: 8px 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Schedule Conflict</h1>
        <p>The tutor or student is already in a session at this time:</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></p>
        <a href="/tasks">Go back to Actions</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
